      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t不会，即使东突厥斯坦的人过来找我认老乡，我也不会认的。<br/>\n我是波兰人，100%Polak，kurwa。在我死之后，请把我的心脏葬在华沙！<br/>\nMarcin的游戏、Hania Rani的琴声、Tarski的真理和Franciszka小姐的歌谣。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTgwYWM5NDQ3NGNhYjg2NGE0MTE4LnBuZz93aWR0aD0yODgmaGVpZ2h0PTM5Mw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/980ac94474cab864a4118.png?width=288&amp;height=393\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/980ac94474cab864a4118.png?width=288&amp;height=393\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/980ac94474cab864a4118.png?width=288&amp;height=393\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTA2NWM3ZWI4OWViOGQxODA3ODk5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e065c7eb89eb8d1807899.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e065c7eb89eb8d1807899.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e065c7eb89eb8d1807899.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjY1ZmY1ODEzMDljYTMzZjExNTUxLnBuZz93aWR0aD05MTUmaGVpZ2h0PTUzNw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b65ff581309ca33f11551.png?width=915&amp;height=537\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b65ff581309ca33f11551.png?width=915&amp;height=537\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b65ff581309ca33f11551.png?width=915&amp;height=537\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWQwOWUyZWFjNDI3NTg2OTMxYzU1LnBuZz93aWR0aD0yMjUmaGVpZ2h0PTMxMg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1d09e2eac427586931c55.png?width=225&amp;height=312\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1d09e2eac427586931c55.png?width=225&amp;height=312\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1d09e2eac427586931c55.png?width=225&amp;height=312\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzI1N2UwNGE5YjAxMzM1NzdmZjk1LnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMzE4JmhlaWdodD04ODM\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7257e04a9b0133577ff95.png?width=1318&amp;height=883\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7257e04a9b0133577ff95.png?width=1318&amp;height=883\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7257e04a9b0133577ff95.png?width=1318&amp;height=883\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOWUwNDA1YjI0ODIwYjY2ZDY5NGRlLnBuZz93aWR0aD0zMTYmaGVpZ2h0PTM4Mg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9e0405b24820b66d694de.png?width=316&amp;height=382\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9e0405b24820b66d694de.png?width=316&amp;height=382\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9e0405b24820b66d694de.png?width=316&amp;height=382\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n但不管怎么说，我认为所有人都是平等的，我会像爱波兰人一样去爱中国人，给予他们同样多的尊重，包括选择生活方式的权利。如果中国人有文化陋习，我将予以批判和帮助他们改正。\t\t</div>",
